                      <br><br>It is also a common fact that most staff who had been parachuted to undertake this role had never undergone any form of training to prepare them for the critical task of hiring right. Using a series of enhanced effective interviewing skills, participants will acquire the skill-sets in making key decisions to place the right people in the right jobs.

